<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrīma</hi>ṉ Em <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>koṇṭaruḷiya <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>Irāyaṟku cellā niṉṟa
<lb n="4"/>varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi> Arpaci mātam <hi rend="grantha"><num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num> §</hi> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaciñka
<lb n="5"/>kulakāla vaḷanāṭṭu teṉpaṉa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṅkāṭṭu nāṭṭup peruṅkōḷi Ūr
<lb n="7"/>mēlaippakuti kīḻaippakutikkum vaṭa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>paṉaiñkāṭṭu vaṭamalai nāṭṭup pūkkuṭi
<lb n="9"/>Araiyarkaḷi <unclear>cōḻaṅkatēvar</unclear> ciṟukkāt
<lb n="10" break="no"/>tāṉ Uḷḷiṭṭārum tirumalaiyār mutali
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yār Uḷḷiṭṭārum Āciriyappiramāṇam
<lb n="12"/>paṇṇikkuṭutta paricāvatu Iṉṉāḷ mutal
<lb n="13"/>cantiṟātittavaraikkum Āciriya naṭakkumiṭa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ttu Uṭaiyār Aḻakiya kulōttuṅkaṟku
<lb n="15"/>Amutupaṭikku <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> racakuṭi vayalil tiṅkaḷ ki
<lb n="16"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> taṉukku
<lb n="17"/><unclear>mē</unclear>laip paṟikālum <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="18"/>Ākattaṭi mūṉṟil Iḻuvaippaṭi kuḻi
<lb n="19"/>nāṉūṟum tāṉattār vēṇṭum
<lb n="20"/>kuṭikku Aṭaittu mutal vantu ko
<lb n="21" break="no"/>ḷḷak kaṭavārkaḷākavum Ippaṭikku
<lb n="22"/>ciṟukkāttā<unclear>ṉ Uḷḷiṭṭārum tina</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="23"/>mutali Uḷḷiṭṭār Eḻuttu<hi rend="grantha">ḥ—</hi> 
